Class ParamDomain

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.AbstractCollection<E>

        • java.util.TreeSet<String>
          • org.fcrepo.server.resourceIndex.ParamDomain
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Cloneable, Iterable<String>, Collection<String>, NavigableSet<String>, Set<String>, SortedSet<String>

    public class ParamDomain
extends TreeSet<String>
    A sorted set of domain values for a parameter. As per the SortedSet contract, iterators over the values in this collection will provide the elements in ascending order.
    Author:
    Chris Wilper
